        <num>CC 3312</num>
        <heading>3312.  Transfer of the secured obligation</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3312.  Transfer of the secured obligation
A transfer of an obligation secured by a mortgage includes the transfer of the mortgage.  In such a case, the transferor warrants the existence, validity and enforceability of the mortgage only to the extent that he warrants the existence, validity, or enforceability of the obligation.</p>
        </content>
